<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17009</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这天是彼得的十岁生日。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17010</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸早上去上班了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但姐姐鲍比、妹妹菲利斯还有他的妈妈都送了他礼物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其中一个礼物是一个火车头模型，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30026</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32631</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得非常开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32632</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得只高兴了三天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40683</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为三天后，火车头突然“砰”的一声，坏掉了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40684</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43089</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得非常伤心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45666</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的姐妹们说他哭了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是彼得坚持说他的眼睛是因为感冒才变红的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51901</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55280</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天晚上爸爸回到家，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55281</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60347</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得把火车头坏掉的事告诉了爸爸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60348</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63395</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸仔细看了看火车头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66555</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “嗯……” 爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66556</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们焦急地等待着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “有修好的希望吗？” 彼得问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76886</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “有，有工具就可以修好，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但不是今晚。” 爸爸愉快地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80823</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85506</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等到星期六，你们帮我一起修吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “女孩儿也能帮忙修火车头吗？” 彼得怀疑地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “当然了！女孩儿和男孩儿一样聪明！” 爸爸说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102459</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“菲利斯，你想不想当火车司机？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102460</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “不想。我的脸会总是脏兮兮的。” 菲利斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “我想我想。” 鲍比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112959</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117274</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爸爸，我长大能当火车司机吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117275</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122247</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “可以，我们会帮你的！” 爸爸回答说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122248</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然有人敲门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “是谁？” 爸爸问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128060</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈走进来，说有两位先生来找爸爸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133097</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136315</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们在隔壁的房间里。” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136316</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“希望他们能快点儿走。孩子们得睡觉了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 但是客人们一直待到很晚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150555</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈给孩子们讲了一个绿眼睛公主的故事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150556</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是隔壁很吵，孩子们听不清楚妈妈讲故事的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸的声音比平时大，而且听起来很生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166672</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女仆露丝走了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166673</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“夫人，先生让您过去一下。” 她对妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172091</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“先生可能有个坏消息要告诉您，请您做好心理准备。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184126</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈去了隔壁房间，他们又说了一会儿话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184127</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，妈妈回来了，脸色苍白。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“该睡觉了。” 她说，“露丝会带你们去睡觉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是你答应过我们可以跟爸爸一起晚睡的！” 菲利斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206749</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “爸爸公司有事，得走了。” 妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206750</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210780</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 孩子们亲了亲妈妈，上床睡觉了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210781</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比没走，她抱住妈妈，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221547</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小声说：“有什么坏消息吗，妈妈？有人……去世了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221548</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有，没人去世。” 妈妈轻轻推开她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235700</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 第二天早上，孩子们醒来以后发现妈妈不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243150</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “我觉得可能是出什么事了。”彼得一边吃早餐一边说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243151</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我问过露丝，她说我们很快就会知道了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “你应该等着问妈妈！” 鲍比生气地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈到家时，已经是晚上七点了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257770</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260275</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看上去很累。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260276</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265174</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她休息了一下，喝了一杯茶，然后说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265175</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孩子们，我有一件事要告诉你们，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>昨晚确实有一个坏消息。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸要离开一段时间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276049</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280297</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我很担心，希望你们能够帮帮妈妈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280298</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283497</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乖乖的，不要吵架。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283498</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287542</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们不知道爸爸为什么要离开。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287543</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到底发生了什么？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>